#

Feta and Spinach Burger

25 min
$10.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

Quick MealHealthyLow-Carb

Description

A savory burger packed with the goodness of spinach and tangy feta cheese, perfect for a quick and satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • ground turkey: 1 pound
  • fresh spinach: 2 cups
  • feta cheese: 1/2 cup, crumbled
  • egg: 1
  • bread crumbs: 1/4 cup
  • burger buns: 4
  • tomato slices: 4 slices
  • lettuce leaves: 4 leaves
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • onion powder: 1 teaspoon
